'''西炒飯'''是[[香港|香港]]的一種[[炒飯|炒飯]]<ref name="hk01-211451">{{cite news |title=西炒飯新手必學零失敗　配料隨意茄汁不可少 |url=https://www.hk01.com/%E9%A3%B2%E9%A3%9F/211451/%E7%82%92%E9%A3%AF%E9%A3%9F%E8%AD%9C-%E8%A5%BF%E7%82%92%E9%A3%AF%E6%96%B0%E6%89%8B%E5%BF%85%E5%AD%B8%E9%9B%B6%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97-%E9%85%8D%E6%96%99%E9%9A%A8%E6%84%8F%E8%8C%84%E6%B1%81%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%B0%91 |accessdate=2019-06-26 |work=香港01 |date=2018-07-17 |archive-date=2019-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626125004/https://www.hk01.com/%E9%A3%B2%E9%A3%9F/211451/%E7%82%92%E9%A3%AF%E9%A3%9F%E8%AD%9C-%E8%A5%BF%E7%82%92%E9%A3%AF%E6%96%B0%E6%89%8B%E5%BF%85%E5%AD%B8%E9%9B%B6%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97-%E9%85%8D%E6%96%99%E9%9A%A8%E6%84%8F%E8%8C%84%E6%B1%81%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%B0%91 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以「西式」為名，卻非源於[[歐洲|歐]][[美洲|美]]地區，而是源於香港的[[茶餐廳|茶餐廳]]<ref>[http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20121125/00500_001.html 食肆炒飯] {{Wayback|url=http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20121125/00500_001.html |date=20191128072322 }}，[[太陽報_(香港)|太陽報 (香港)]]，2012-11-25</ref>，這款炒飯在[[大牌檔|大牌檔]]和[[港式快餐|港式快餐]]店在午飯和晚飯時間亦有提供。西炒飯的主要特色是成本低廉，雖然炒飯的配料通常包括肉類，但較少用上新鮮肉食，而是使用切片或切成粒狀的[[雞肉腸|雞肉腸]]、[[火腿|火腿]]或[[午餐肉|午餐肉]]<ref name="港式西炒飯">{{cite news |title=3步港式西炒飯食譜 新手零失敗還原茶餐廳風味 |url=https://food.ulifestyle.com.hk/recipe/detail/3039698/%E7%82%92%E9%A3%AF%E9%A3%9F%E8%AD%9C-3%E6%AD%A5%E6%B8%AF%E5%BC%8F%E8%A5%BF%E7%82%92%E9%A3%AF%E9%A3%9F%E8%AD%9C-%E6%96%B0%E6%89%8B%E9%9B%B6%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E9%82%84%E5%8E%9F%E8%8C%B6%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E9%A2%A8%E5%91%B3 |accessdate=2022-03-12 |work=U Food |date=2021-08-23 |archive-date=2022-03-12 |archive-url=https://archive.fo/LBp0O |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==製作==
西炒飯不同於其他地區的番茄汁炒飯，其特色是如同[[揚州炒飯|揚州炒飯]]將各種配料和米飯一起炒。至於用料上沒有既定標準，但必須要有[[番茄醬|番茄醬]]，使其有紅色的外表。由於番茄乃源於西方的食材，故[[香港英治時期|港英時期]]的香港人給予此稱呼。除了[[白飯|白飯]]和[[雞蛋|雞蛋]]之外<ref>{{cite web |title=港式西炒飯 |url=https://family.esdlife.com/recipe/detail/2451 |website=family.esdlife.com |accessdate=2019-06-26 |archive-date=2019-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191106155544/https://family.esdlife.com/recipe/detail/2451 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，配料通常包括[[香腸|香腸]]粒及[[火腿|火腿]]粒，以及[[番茄|番茄]]、[[洋蔥|洋蔥]]、[[蘑菇|蘑菇]]等<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hkhselderly.com/tc/food/recipes/257|title=家常健康西炒飯|work=房協長者通|date=2012-04-19|access-date=2015-01-29|archive-date=2019-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210035509/https://www.hkhselderly.com/tc/food/recipes/257|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另外，西炒飯在香港部分茶餐廳又名「衰人炒飯」，因為西人與衰人近音而得名<ref>{{cite news |title=【餓底需知】茶餐廳粥粉麵飯代號（上) |url=https://news.now.com/home/life/player?newsId=242541 |accessdate=2019-12-19 |work=Now新聞 |date=2017-11-09 |archive-date=2019-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191219115313/https://news.now.com/home/life/player%3FnewsId%3D242541 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

